msg: test processes seem to interfere with each other

author: veithen
msg: Renamed OMImplementation to OMMetaFactory and converted it from an abstract class to an interface. This will be useful for OSGIification (OSGi will require an interface here). Eliminating OMImplementation is OK because
- it only exists in the 1.2.8 release;
- it was not yet complete (no getInstance method);
- it was only used in the test cases;
- we can easily put it back if somebody complains.
